td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Article 29 of the Act concerning the Conditions of Accession of the Kingdom of Denmark, Ireland and the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland and the Adjustments to the Treaties (OJ, English Special Edition of 27 March 1972, p. 14; ‘the 1972 Act of Accession’), read in conjunction with point 4 of Section I of Annex I thereto, and the interpretation and validity of Article 12(2) of Council Directive 91/477/EEC of 18 June 1991 on control of the acquisition and possession of weapons (
OJ 1991 L 256, p. 51
), as amended by Directive 2008/51/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 21 May 2008 (
OJ 2008 L 179, p. 5
) (‘Directive 91/477’).
